```

## How to Use Types

Types can be imported and used to strongly type your controllers, services, and API responses:

```typescript
import type { ApiProductProduct } from '../../../types/generated/contentTypes';

// Using types in a service
export default {
  async findProducts(): Promise<ApiProductProduct[]> {
    const products = await strapi.entityService.findMany('api::product.product', {
      populate: ['product_variations', 'product_main_category'],
    });
    return products;
  }
}
```
